---
title: Red Thai Style Prawn Coconut Udon Soup with Pak Choi and Mushrooms
description: Red chillies give Thai Red its signature colour, as well as its flavour and heat! Here, our Red Thai Style Prawn Coconut Udon Soup is loaded with veg and thick udon noodles in a curried coconut milk base.
